data.description: Instantly appealing, practically new, craftsman home with modern farmhouse finishes situated perfectly on a level, corner lot minutes from downtown Toccoa. Upon arrival you'll be taken back by the abundance of upgrades including a combination of board & batten and lap siding, striking paint choices, new roof with architectural shingles, and wonderful outdoor spaces. The interior includes an open floor plan featuring master on main, beautiful luxury vinyl flooring, fireplace with brick facade, granite counter tops, and stainless-steel appliances! This beautiful home includes a full unfinished daylight basement perfect for an expanding family or extra storage! Prepared to be wowed!
